						               													<description>Bearly Surviving is a turn-based strategy board game, where players are given workers that double as their health. The more workers players have, the more resources they get each turn, and the faster they can build a colossal army to destroy their opponents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Through action cards, Bearly Surviving offers unique battle mechanics that are easy to learn but hard to master. Players need to efficiently use their resources and cleverly utilise their units to plan and react to their opponent&amp;rsquo;s move to destroy their enemies.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During your turn, you collect resources depending on how you distributed your workers in your previous turn. So thinking ahead is very important in this game. These resources help you build up a strong army that you can use to attack other players with the help of the action cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;An attack on another player not only damages their army but also their workers. Once a player has no more workers, they are eliminated from the game. The game ends when a player either collects all ROAR cards or eliminates all other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
